reviewText: life changing..... life altering....  life AFFIRMING!
Probably one of the best Christian videos I have ever seen for real.
In my opinion, this is an excellently presented non-judgmental testimonial.  I was very impressed with the compassion and grace expressed by each of the participants.

I found this very sincere and comforting to know that there are other Mormon converts out there that slowly discovered the truth.  I could relate to her devastation as her world fell apart but how she was lifted up again by the truth of the Gospel of Jesus Christ.  Kudos to her for writing this.

This was a beautiful honest story of these 8 seeking truth and finding it outside of the religion they thought was true. It is very sweet and not abrasive at all. A heart warming about people seeking God. Loved it
